item.title: CVE-2023-0279|2023-02-27T15:24:39.076Z -- unknown -- media%20library%20assistant
item.description: The Media Library Assistant WordPress plugin before 3.06 does not properly sanitise and escape a parameter before using it in a SQL statement, leading to a SQL injection exploitable by high privilege users such as admin.
